<subSubSection pageId="255" pageNumber="860" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="255.[1452,2661,1315,2175]" pageId="255" pageNumber="860">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1454,1801,1945,1979]" pageId="255" pageNumber="860">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Vulnerable on The IUCN Red List. The Mentawai Archipelago Spiny Rat has a relatively small distribution and is threatened by habitat destruction from logging. It occurs in Siberut National Park on Siberut. Additional research is needed to fully understand its natural history, taxonomy, and threats.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
